      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-6">
          Built-In Webhook Integration
        </h2>
        <div
          class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted leading-relaxed"
        >
          <p>
            CalendHub includes webhook integration as a built-in feature that
            powers seamless connectivity with your other business tools. When
            appointments are created, updated, or cancelled, CalendHub
            automatically sends real-time notifications to connected systems.
            This happens behind the scenes without any setup or configuration
            needed from you. Your CRM, automation tools, and integrated
            applications receive appointment data instantly, keeping everything
            synchronized automatically.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike systems that require you to constantly check for updates or
            manually export data, CalendHub's webhook system proactively pushes
            information to your connected tools the moment events happen. When a
            customer books an appointment, your CRM gets updated immediately.
            When someone reschedules, your Google Calendar syncs instantly. When
            an appointment is cancelled, your Zoom meeting link is removed
            automatically. Everything stays synchronized in real-time without
            you lifting a finger.
          </p>

          <p>
            This built-in integration capability enables powerful automation
            workflows without complex setup. Connect your Google Calendar, Zoom
            meetings, and LinkedIn profile, and appointment data flows
            automatically. Calendar events sync to Google Calendar instantly.
            Video meeting links from Zoom generate automatically for virtual
            appointments. LinkedIn posts can be scheduled alongside your
            appointments. All of this works out of the box as part of
            CalendHub's core functionality, with more integrations coming soon.
          </p>

          <p>
            CalendHub's webhook infrastructure runs reliably in the background,
            handling all the technical complexity of real-time data
            synchronization. The system manages delivery, automatically retries
            if connections are temporarily unavailable, and ensures no
            appointment data is lost. Built-in integrations with Google
            Calendar, Zoom, and LinkedIn provide the real-time connectivity your
            business needs without requiring technical expertise or manual
            configuration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
